examples: when he yawned I could see the gold fillings in his teeth
an informal British term for `filling' is `stopping'

definition: the act of filling something
name: filling

definition: a service station that sells gasoline
name: filling station

definition: anything that tends to arouse
name: fillip
examples: his approval was an added fillip

definition: elected vice president and became the 13th President of the United States when Zachary Taylor died in office (1800-1874)
name: Fillmore

definition: a young female horse under the age of four
name: filly

definition: a form of entertainment that enacts a story by sound and a sequence of images giving the illusion of continuous movement
name: film
examples: the film was shot on location
